title: #92Noon! Montage/Bercich/Siny/Cronin/Talkers
description: Most of the show is spent analyzing the 27-6 Bill beatdown from yesterday with Bercich in studio early on and ESPN's Courtney Cronin making an appearance during the final hour. Dave Sinykin on the border battle, some calls and more!
